1
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,280
Young General, are you there?

2
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,880
The General wants to see you.

3
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,240
Young General.

4
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,520
This kid's breathing is chaotic.

5
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,840
He is indeed very weak.

6
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:29,280
Whether he colluded with Ji Mingyue,

7
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:32,479
and whether he is from the Helian clan,

8
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:34,039
let's test him.

9
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,200
General,

10
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,200
please save our Young General.

11
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,600
Jiuying is my beloved general.

12
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,380
I will naturally save him.

13
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:46,960
Guards.

14
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,080
Yes.

15
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,880
Send Jiuying to Wuse City.

16
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:53,259
There is a royal doctor from the capital in the city.

17
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,560
Let him treat Jiuying well.

18
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,360
Don't let anything go wrong.

19
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,400
Yes, sir.

20
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,240
Your Highness, I've brought

21
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,810
the thing you asked for.

22
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,640
This edict is real.

23
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,460
Huo Lingyu is from the Hanlin Academy

24
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,120
and has seen many edicts.

25
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,640
Even he couldn't find any problems.

26
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,120
It seems that my posthumous edict

27
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,880
is completely convincing.

28
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,480
Hahaha.

29
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,340
Your Highness.

30
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,360
You were so hard to find.

31
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,000
General Baili,

32
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,120
I trust you've been well.

33
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,960
The late Emperor's edict is right here.

34
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:04,720
Now,

35
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,700
the Shenji Camp is in my hands,

36
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,060
and the military tally is in my hands too.

37
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:12,080
What will General Baili do?

38
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,200
You need to think clearly.

39
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,089
[Cheng Se Wu]

40
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,080
The Imperial Physician has returned to the capital.

41
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,840
Yes.

42
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:31,720
Three days ago, an urgent edict suddenly arrived from the capital.

43
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,200
The Imperial Physician then returned with the envoy.

44
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,480
Your Young Master Helian was born frail.

45
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:39,080
The court sent the Imperial Physician to prolong his life.

46
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,520
Now that the Imperial Physician is gone,

47
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,280
what about your Young Master's injuries?

48
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,340
Who will treat him?

49
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,200
I don't know.

50
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,680
To treat the Young Master,

51
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:52,210
the High Priest has been in seclusion with him for several days.

52
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,800
The General ordered before his departure

53
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,920
that after the Young General arrives at the Helian Clan,

54
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,000
he would dispatch troops to surround Wuse City.

55
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,360
If the Young General shows any hesitation,

56
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,960
he is to be killed on the spot.

57
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:11,780
I presume the General's elite troops will arrive shortly.

58
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,620
General, have you thought this through?

59
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,970
The military tally was stolen.

60
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:32,120
The late emperor's edict's authenticity is unknown.

61
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:36,380
Actually, you only have the Shenji Battalion under your command, right?

62
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:41,020
There is no point in you talking like this, General.

63
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,680
If I were of no use,

64
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,800
why would you eagerly invite me to the North?

65
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,760
General Baili.

66
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,760
With me here,

67
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:56,450
your march on the Capital will be completely justified.

68
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,920
Without me,

69
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,060
you are nothing but a traitor.

70
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,040
As for the military tally...

71
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:07,400
Then it depends on how the general acts.

72
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,800
How dare you threaten me?

73
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,280
So what if I threaten you?

74
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,320
Bring them up.

75
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,280
Yes.

76
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,360
Bring the military seal first.

77
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,560
So this is the legendary Eagle Eye.

78
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:47,080
I really don't like the look of it.

79
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:50,080
Why don't I gouge it out?

80
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,360
I hate you the most,

81
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,560
but I am also most gratified to have raised you.

82
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,000
You are more like me than Jin.

83
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:08,920
We women of the Shen family never bow to men,

84
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,480
refuse to be threatened,

85
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:15,280
and don't accept fate.

86
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:31,240
Don't even think

87
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:35,559
about using me to threaten anyone.

88
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,280
Hmph.

89
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,160
Your Highness,

90
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:49,160
you are truly a master of politics.

91
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:53,040
To remain unfazed while your own mother dies before your eyes,

92
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,420
you are indeed heartless enough.

93
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,880
Done showing off?

94
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,960
Now,

95
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,280
it's time to sit down and discuss cooperation.

96
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:42,720
We women of the Shen family never bow to men,

97
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,280
refuse to be threatened,

98
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,320
and do not yield to fate.

99
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:09,170
Helian Jin's antidote hasn't been found yet.

100
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,770
He will likely continue to be controlled by Baili Jinghong.

101
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,840
I shouldn't have pinned my hopes on him.

102
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,880
Eldest Young Master.

103
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,040
Eldest Young Master.

104
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:43,080
The general's spies are all around the mansion.

105
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,280
I can't get out at all.

106
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,440
Right now,

107
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:49,140
we have no way to know the Second Young Master's situation.

108
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,200
I must go see Aman

109
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,440
and Mingyue.

110
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,300
I came so suddenly.

111
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,680
I'm afraid I won't make it back within three days.

112
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,210
I need to send her a message.

113
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,560
Cover for me for a bit.

114
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,780
I'll be right back.

115
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,040
Eldest Young Master,

116
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:07,440
are you going to use your secret arts again?

117
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,480
If Her Highness treated you

118
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,480
even a third as well as you treat her,

119
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,570
I wouldn't be so worried about you.

120
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,320
Father.

121
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,880
What are you doing?

122
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,640
I have tried everything.

123
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,960
But failed.

124
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,480
I am old.

125
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:58,160
It is worth trading my life for yours.

126
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,560
No.

127
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,520
It's retribution.

128
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,560
Haven't you always wanted to know

129
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:07,240
how your eldest brother left back then?

130
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,080
Back then,

131
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,240
you were weak and sick.

132
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:14,820
And I still held a grudge against his mother.

133
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,520
When he was fifteen,

134
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:21,960
I plotted to transfer his blood to you.

135
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,800
So you wouldn't have to suffer physical pain

136
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,760
and be in agony anymore.

137
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,920
But he was truly strong.

138
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:35,080
At such a young age, his skills were extraordinary.

139
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:38,360
Facing the siege of the ten deadly assassins of the Helian clan,

140
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,280
he still managed to escape.

141
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:45,080
He guessed someone in the clan wanted his life,

142
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:48,760
so he fled overnight.

143
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,680
Father.

144
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,320
Father.

145
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,280
Man'er.

146
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,800
Remember my words.

147
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:02,320
No one will truly protect us.

148
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:05,760
Always leave a way out for yourself.

149
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,120
An innocent man

150
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,600
is ruined by his wealth.

151
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,320
My Helian clan,

152
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:18,400
how did it come to this?

153
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,400
Father.

154
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:23,800
Father.

155
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,480
Father.

156
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,160
Father.

157
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,200
Father.

158
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:38,840
Father.

159
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,200
Father.

160
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,000
Brother.

161
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:45,880
Hurry.

162
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,160
Hurry.

163
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:47,890
Stop Father!

164
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,400
Brother.

165
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,360
Are you okay?

166
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:53,960
Brother.

167
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,720
Save Father quickly!

168
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:01,680
Don't waste your effort. Father.

169
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,320
Once this method starts,

170
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:06,620
it cannot be interrupted.

171
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,320
Trading life for life.

172
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:12,800
Are you going to watch

173
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:15,240
your brother die?

174
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,840
What secret art is this?

175
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,960
Trading life for life.

176
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,320
Mother.

177
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,780
No wonder my poison was cured.

178
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,880
You came back

179
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,400
to ask how to save her?

180
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:38,120
She can't be saved.

181
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:42,200
This method is irreversible.

182
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,200
Don't even think about

183
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,800
returning it.

184
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,040
Father.

185
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:59,280
Father.

186
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,240
Father.

187
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:04,680
Father.

188
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,120
Wu Lie said

189
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,900
when he first met you, Your Highness,

190
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:26,120
you were traveling with Jiuying,

191
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,560
digging a gold mine for the bandits of Mount Beimang.

192
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:33,000
Now the gold has been refined,

193
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,380
and the quality is quite good.

194
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,720
General, you have many strong soldiers

195
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:40,700
and wealth rivaling a nation.

196
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,600
I am impressed.

197
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:48,660
Helian Jie captured you, Your Highness.

198
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,780
You have suffered a great injustice.

199
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:52,480
Rest assured.

200
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:56,320
I have already dispatched troops to Wuse City,

201
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,490
and ordered Jiuying to accompany them

202
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:03,960
to capture the High Priest and Helian Jie,

203
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,840
and vent this anger for you, Your Highness.
